#: ../../T/TOPS-10.rst:5
msgid "TOPS-10"
msgstr "TOPS-10"

#: ../../T/TOPS-10.rst:7
msgid "/tops·ten/, n\\."
msgstr "/tops·ten/, 名詞"

#: ../../T/TOPS-10.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`DEC`\\'s proprietary OS for the fabled :ref:`PDP-10` machines, long a "
"favorite of hackers but now long extinct. A fountain of hacker folklore; see"
" Appendix A. See also :ref:`ITS`\\, :ref:`TOPS-20`\\, :ref:`TWENEX`\\, "
":ref:`VMS`\\, :ref:`operating-system`\\. TOPS-10 was sometimes called "
"BOTS-10 (from ‘bottoms-ten’) as a comment on the inappropriateness of "
"describing it as the top of anything."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`DEC`\\ の、伝説的な\\ :ref:`PDP-10`\\ "
"マシン向けの独自OS。長らくハッカーのお気に入りだったが、今ではとうに絶滅した。ハッカー伝承の泉である。付録A参照。\\ :ref:`ITS`\\ "
"、\\ :ref:`TOPS-20`\\ 、\\ :ref:`TWENEX`\\ 、\\ :ref:`VMS`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`operating-system`\\ "
"も参照。TOPS-10は、何かの頂点(top)と称するのが不適切だという皮肉として、BOTS-10(‘bottoms-"
"ten’から)と呼ばれることもあった。"
